question: الي أخذوا كيميكل رآكشن إيش كان Reference book?
هل في خبر الى الان عند مود الدراسه بعد رمضان بالنسبه لتخصصنا او لسى ماقرروً
شباب ذي الرساله ارسلوها في قروب التيليجرام ، هل ضروري نعبيها؟
answer: It is informed that the Center for Academic and Learning Experiences (CAEL) under the Graduate Institute for Available Life (UTM iLeague) is in the process of collecting statistical information on undergraduate students up to the 2021/22 cohort who have not yet taken general university courses. Accordingly, students are required to fill out a questionnaire on student registration for general university courses. Updating the information in the google form must be done no later than April 20, 2022.
